Package: AGBootstrap
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Generative Bootstrap for Small-Sample Inference
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Saifuldeen", "Dheyauldeen Alrefaee",
           email = "saifuldeen.alrefaee@uomosul.edu.iq",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
)
Description: Implements the Adaptive Generative Bootstrap (AGB) method to improve
    coverage probability in small-sample and multimodal settings. Variable-bandwidth
    kernel density estimation is combined with generative resampling to produce
    robust bootstrap replicates.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
